title: Trump fires Acting AG for not enforcing immigration ban
text:
Trump fires Acting AG for not enforcing immigration ban Jan. 31, 2017 - 7:30 - Sarah Isgur Flores, Spokesperson for Attorney General nominee Sessions, on President Trump firing Acting Attorney General Sally Yates, the confirmation hearing for Attorney General nominee Jeff Sessions and Trump's potential Supreme Court Justice nomination.
